<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:19:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>布林肯表示，他预计朝鲜士兵将在未来几天内部署对抗乌克兰军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/blinken-says-he-expects-north-korean-soldiers-deploy-against-ukrainian-forces-2024-10-31/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周四表示，美国预计在俄罗斯的朝鲜士兵将在未来几天内部署以对抗乌克兰军队，并警告说，如果他们参与针对基辅的战斗，他们将成为合法的军事目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/blinken-says-he-expects-north-korean-soldiers-deploy-against-ukrainian-forces-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国称8000名朝鲜军队驻扎在俄罗斯库尔斯克</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/us-says-8000-north-korean-troops-russias-kursk-2024-10-31/</link><description>美国驻联合国副大使罗伯特·伍德周四对安理会表示，美国收到的信息表明，“目前”在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区有 8000 名朝鲜军队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 17:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/us-says-8000-north-korean-troops-russias-kursk-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会要求周一就朝鲜导弹发射问题举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/un-security-council-asked-meet-monday-north-korea-missile-launch-2024-10-31/</link><description>两位外交官表示，联合国安理会可能会在周一就朝鲜周四进行的试验（平壤所说的洲际弹道导弹）问题举行会议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 16:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/un-security-council-asked-meet-monday-north-korea-missile-launch-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>信中显示，民主党议员就华为产品中的台积电芯片问题向拜登发起攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-lawmaker-takes-aim-biden-over-tsmc-chip-huawei-product-document-shows-2024-10-31/</link><description>民主党参议员马克·沃纳 (Mark Warner) 批评拜登政府对台积电的“监控明显松懈”，此前有报道称，这家台湾芯片制造商生产的芯片最终被用于中国受到严厉制裁的华为生产的产品中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 13:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-lawmaker-takes-aim-biden-over-tsmc-chip-huawei-product-document-shows-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>政府支持的媒体称，中国工商总局否认与欧盟就电动汽车进行谈判的报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-denies-reports-negotiations-with-eu-evs-govt-backed-media-says-2024-10-31/</link><description>据当地政府支持的《上海观察家报》周四报道，中国上汽集团被欧盟征收最高的电动汽车附加关税（35.3%），该公司驳斥了有关与欧盟就此事单独谈判的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 11:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-denies-reports-negotiations-with-eu-evs-govt-backed-media-says-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>国际清算银行将退出中国支持的央行数字货币项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bis-leave-cross-border-payments-platform-project-mbridge-2024-10-31/</link><description>国际清算银行周四表示，将退出跨境支付平台 Project mBridge，这引发了人们的疑问：在全球转账的地缘政治审查日益严格之际，中国支持的这一计划将如何演变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 11:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bis-leave-cross-border-payments-platform-project-mbridge-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>越南敦促中国释放在南海被扣押的渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-china-release-detained-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-31/</link><description>外交部发言人周四表示，越南对中国在南海有争议的西沙群岛扣留越南渔民和渔船的行为提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-china-release-detained-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>默克预计加德西中国的困境将持续至 2025 年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-third-quarter-better-than-expected-gardasil-sales-sag-china-again-2024-10-31/</link><description>默克公司周四表示，加德西 (Gardasil) 在中国的销售疲软可能会持续到 2025 年，因为该疫苗的经销商在需求低迷的情况下减少了库存，这家美国制药商的股价下跌了 3%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-third-quarter-better-than-expected-gardasil-sales-sag-china-again-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>官员称印尼将对南海事件做出适当反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四，在一艘中国海警船中断雅加达国有能源公司的调查后，印尼在南海问题上的立场保持不变，并将采取适当行动以保护其领土。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”袭来，上海迎来暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</link><description>中国金融中心上海正面临40多年来最严重的降雨，台风“康瑞”预计将从南部登陆，并在未来两天席卷东部沿海。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>据Politico报道，美国通过与中国公民的交易确保牧师从中国获释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</link><description>据《Politico》周三援引三名知情人士的话报道，美国上个月以一名中国公民为条件，从中国释放了美国牧师林大卫 (David Lin)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国10月非制造业活动恢复扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四的一项官方调查显示，中国十月份非制造业活动有所扩张，这让政策制定者松了一口气，尽管其他指标表明世界第二大经济体的复苏仍然遥远。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造业活动六个月来首次扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</link><description>十月份服务业也有所回升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺老板表示，欧盟根据世贸组织规则对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-cars-based-wto-rules-renault-boss-says-2024-10-30/</link><description>法国汽车制造商雷诺首席执行官卢卡·德·梅奥表示，欧盟周三对中国进口电动汽车征收的关税是基于世界贸易组织制定的规则，每个人都签署了这些规则。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-cars-based-wto-rules-renault-boss-says-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求汽车制造商暂停对支持电动汽车关税的欧盟国家的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-carmakers-pause-investment-eu-countries-backing-ev-tariffs-sources-2024-10-30/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国已要求其汽车制造商停止对支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税的欧洲国家进行大规模投资，此举可能会进一步分裂欧洲。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-carmakers-pause-investment-eu-countries-backing-ev-tariffs-sources-2024-10-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>